<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577678>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Photographs and schematic dorsal views of Pelecocera heads, showing the shape of the swollen part of the vertex in females of A: P. scaevoides, B: P. pruinosomaculata, C: P. lugubris, D: P. garrigae sp. nov. and E: P. caledonica." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6577678/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577668>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pelecocera garrigae sp. nov. paratype female: A: head and abdomen: lateral view, B head frontal view, C: head, dorso-lateral view, D and E: abdomen: dorsal views. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6577668/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577680>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Head, lateral view, A: Pelecocera tricincta, B: Pelecocera garrigae sp. nov.." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6577680/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577682>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Head, frontal view to show parafaces (arrow) of different Pelecocera species from France.A. Pelecocera lugubris, B: Pelecocera garrigae sp. nov., C: Pelecocera scaevoides, D: Pelecocera pruinosomaculata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6577682/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577686>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Head semi-lateral view to show the lunules (arrow) of: A. Pelecocera lugubris, B: Pelecocera garrigae sp. nov., C: Pelecocera scaevoides, D: Pelecocera pruinosomaculata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6577686/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

